winning_structure.name: UBX-ESF-INS
winning_structure.description: This message outputs information about the vehicle dynamics. The output dynamics information (angular rates and accelerations) are expressed with respect to the vehicle-frame.

bits.name: version
bits.description: Message version (0x01 for this version)

bits.name: xAngRateValid
bits.description: Compensated x-axis angular rate data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: yAngRateValid
bits.description: Compensated y-axis angular rate data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: zAngRateValid
bits.description: Compensated z-axis angular rate data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: xAccelValid
bits.description: Compensated x-axis acceleration data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: yAccelValid
bits.description: Compensated y-axis acceleration data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: zAccelValid
bits.description: Compensated z-axis acceleration data validity flag (0: not valid, 1: valid).

bits.name: reserved1
bits.description: Reserved

fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See the section iTOW timestamps in Integration manual for details.
